{"tid":1448504,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"之前警察唔敢混入去，係因為呢招一比人發現就絕對返唔到轉頭","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:34:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T16:57:15.000Z","uid":161430,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"6bc3b81eaacae6253da697ebee7907c1135834f0","tid":1448504,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:34:01.000Z","msg":"過期催淚彈你可以賴死唔認<br />\n搵公安武警幫手你可以賴死唔認<br />\n搵黑社會你可以賴死話警察冇同佢地合作<br />\n冇人會fact check倒，最多9成知多數係事實，<br />\n但除非警察自己自爆，否則證實唔倒<br />\n<br />\n但係搵香港警察自己混入示威者，一比人發現同起埋底，核對好之後，<br />\nfact check埋，就冇話你認唔認 已經係100%事實<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vxZmxjw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvxZmxjw.png&h=1d33d451&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以之前鄧柄強先冇用呢招，宜家新官上任即用呢招又即時自爆，<br />\n究竟算係聰明定係蠢？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">點都好，總之宜家香港已經回唔到頭</span>"},{"pid":"61bc3719e64a8ac8d9683241c22985c3bd5f26da","tid":1448504,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:34:51.000Z","msg":"玩完"},{"pid":"bf13c19585f6ea0903ed3c956a2a00f861e2d401","tid":1448504,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:35:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d00703afda1d29b4af63a4f30caa37f9ccf93dfa","tid":1448504,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:36:13.000Z","msg":"老豆搵仔，搵到扮示威者飛虎隊成員<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1447168\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1447168</a><br />\n- 分享